<br>
Gen <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uzavyynmatrisyan.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Zavyyn Matrisyan</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br>  Posts: 19<br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/30/01 11:40 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Patch of Shadow</span><hr size=1> i got mine from the shadowed man camp in WC...  i went there and a lvl 50+ rogue was camping for jboots...  he went ahead and grouped with me and went about killing with me helping some...  i got a patch before he got his rapier /shrug<br>
